WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

01:25.188 --> 01:31.620
【The fate that cannot be liberated】

01:31.620 --> 01:34.468
[Episode 23]

01:35.680 --> 01:38.959
Why do you think bandits
have anything to do with me?

01:39.799 --> 01:42.560
Someone ambushed you on the hunting grounds.

01:43.719 --> 01:45.000
This never happened.

01:45.000 --> 01:46.079
Does it also have something to do with me?

01:47.640 --> 01:49.640
You know everyone in this palace,
except Wang Dequan,

01:50.239 --> 01:52.860
He is an old servant of the former emperor.

01:52.860 --> 01:55.400
The rest is all brought by you.

01:56.319 --> 01:58.159
How did I pull them off?

01:58.799 --> 02:00.159
No one knows?

02:01.920 --> 02:04.040
What about military tokens?

02:04.959 --> 02:06.720
since you became regent

02:06.720 --> 02:08.360
The He family was wiped out.

02:09.319 --> 02:10.620
The Yan family was sent to Sichuan

02:10.620 --> 02:12.120
After the hunt.

02:12.120 --> 02:13.199
Which of them doesn't want it?

02:14.120 --> 02:15.360
Why do you think it's me?

02:16.520 --> 02:17.639
You are my uncle.

02:18.439 --> 02:20.759
Your Majesty, there is no need to quibble.

02:21.400 --> 02:23.360
But you should know about the He family.

02:23.360 --> 02:26.020
I'm more concerned about

02:26.020 --> 02:27.560
These are dangerous and unpredictable situations.

02:28.199 --> 02:29.819
Do you admit it?

02:29.819 --> 02:32.680
Did you frame the entire He family?

02:35.639 --> 02:38.700
Your Majesty has been in poor health recently.

02:38.700 --> 02:41.560
Rest in the palace from now on.

02:42.159 --> 02:45.000
You don't need to worry about anything else.

02:45.840 --> 02:47.120
Do you want to put me under house arrest?

02:48.000 --> 02:49.024
No.

02:50.840 --> 02:51.872
I just

02:52.840 --> 02:54.700
Try sharing your concerns.

02:54.700 --> 02:57.120
How...how dare you?

02:57.879 --> 02:58.912
guard!

02:59.919 --> 03:00.928
Where are the guards?

03:01.840 --> 03:02.848
guard!

03:06.560 --> 03:07.584
You bastard!

03:07.584 --> 03:08.608
Your Majesty,

03:09.199 --> 03:10.439
Do you know how to curse now?

03:12.960 --> 03:14.480
I'm too kind.

03:14.480 --> 03:17.599
I convinced the bird that it had strong wings.

03:18.759 --> 03:22.160
Since you think you are an eagle,
I will put you in a cage

03:22.160 --> 03:23.264
so you know

03:23.960 --> 03:25.719
You are just a caged bird.

03:28.879 --> 03:29.984
Rong Yu,

03:32.319 --> 03:34.340
You said I'm not the person you're destined to be

03:34.340 --> 03:36.039
And I am not on your marriage line.

03:36.560 --> 03:38.780
So why no matter
how we wander

03:38.780 --> 03:40.000
Even if we are thousands of miles apart,

03:41.000 --> 03:42.360
I still married you

03:43.008 --> 03:44.128
And fell in love with you?

03:44.680 --> 03:46.080
Isn't this fate?

03:47.680 --> 03:48.736
I can't imagine that future

03:49.759 --> 03:52.920
With anyone but you.

03:52.920 --> 03:54.159
Just be a general.

03:54.759 --> 03:55.800
The future General Rong.

03:56.479 --> 03:57.536
Your General Xiaorong.

03:58.520 --> 04:00.260
What if she was a girl?

04:00.260 --> 04:02.140
We will pamper her to no end.

04:02.140 --> 04:04.620
Not to mention ten years, not even a day,

04:04.620 --> 04:07.159
Do we want her to leave us and go to Mount Wuhua to suffer?

04:07.840 --> 04:10.944
Thinking of our General Xiaorong
or Miss Xiaorong

04:11.680 --> 04:13.520
Let my heart sing.

04:15.159 --> 04:17.280
Usually, it's you who runs to me.

04:17.280 --> 04:19.160
Can I finally
contact you this time?

04:24.759 --> 04:27.160
Normally, I don't
give people second chances.

04:28.600 --> 04:32.120
But for you,
I am willing to give countless opportunities.

04:34.279 --> 04:35.680
I've run to you.

04:36.360 --> 04:37.600
if you still love me

04:38.399 --> 04:39.900
Just stretch out your hand,

04:39.900 --> 04:41.859
I am willing to give you all my love

04:41.859 --> 04:43.800
And sincerity for the rest of my life.

04:46.240 --> 04:47.328
What if I told you

04:52.839 --> 04:54.048
I do not like you anymore?

05:01.120 --> 05:03.380
Then why did you rush into the fire to save me?

05:03.380 --> 05:04.519
The fire was so intense.

05:05.040 --> 05:06.200
I can't even escape myself.

05:06.200 --> 05:07.220
Why did you do that?

05:07.220 --> 05:09.240
I will save anyone without hesitation

05:10.560 --> 05:11.616
Inside the Astrology Hall.

05:12.759 --> 05:14.279
I can't stand idly by

05:15.199 --> 05:16.224
And watching someone die in front of me.

05:17.519 --> 05:18.560
but…

05:19.480 --> 05:23.759
Since you are so upright and noble,

05:25.319 --> 05:26.920
why are you going to all this trouble

05:26.920 --> 05:29.120
Eliminate everyone who is harmful to me?

05:31.480 --> 05:32.544
All I did was help the emperor

05:33.360 --> 05:35.160
Destroy the bad guys as quickly as possible.

05:37.399 --> 05:38.399
I didn't think too much about it.

05:46.120 --> 05:47.879
School is out! School is out!

05:50.600 --> 05:54.040
Master, I want to
pray for Xingxiang Pavilion tonight.

05:54.040 --> 05:56.319
Can you tell me what to say?

05:59.759 --> 06:01.319
OK Go play.

06:01.920 --> 06:02.944
Thank you Master.

06:03.560 --> 06:04.839
let's go. Let's go play together.

06:07.160 --> 06:08.224
OK

06:14.839 --> 06:16.040
When I'm sick and confused,

06:16.920 --> 06:18.016
I only recognized you.

06:18.720 --> 06:19.959
That will definitely give you false hope,

06:20.680 --> 06:21.879
But this is just an illusion.

06:32.759 --> 06:33.824
He Jiuling.

06:34.439 --> 06:35.488
why do you think

06:36.519 --> 06:38.600
i will still love you

06:39.920 --> 06:40.928
After knowing that you burned down my Xingxiang Pavilion?

06:44.519 --> 06:47.199
Did Madam run to put out the fire?

06:47.839 --> 06:48.928
that's right.

06:49.680 --> 06:50.720
correct?

07:04.439 --> 07:07.279
Your Highness,
the Emperor is not having an easy time right now.

07:07.839 --> 07:10.060
As Jialin’s mainstay,

07:10.060 --> 07:12.576
Please give me more guidance in the future.

07:13.152 --> 07:14.180
please.

07:14.180 --> 07:15.744
——Master, the young master is back!
- This is…

07:17.800 --> 07:18.816
minute.

07:18.816 --> 07:19.968
Father.

07:22.560 --> 07:23.680
Father.

07:24.480 --> 07:25.536
what happened?

07:36.319 --> 07:37.560
Master Rong said I won’t see you again.

07:37.560 --> 07:38.944
All these things are yours.

07:39.456 --> 07:40.512
You can take them away.

07:41.120 --> 07:43.199
If you don't want them,
I'll have them thrown away.

07:44.639 --> 07:45.800
Zhanping.

07:50.176 --> 07:51.220
I -

07:51.220 --> 07:52.224
Stop talking.

07:52.800 --> 07:54.279
I don't know how to face you now.

07:55.040 --> 07:56.519
Teacher Rong is so kind to you.

07:57.079 --> 07:58.839
Why do you want to hurt him like this?

07:59.720 --> 08:02.624
If you are going through something,
you can tell us.

08:03.560 --> 08:05.560
Do you know
how important Xingxiang Pavilion is to him?

08:07.399 --> 08:08.448
forget it.

08:09.199 --> 08:11.840
This is the money Master Rong has prepared for you.
You should leave.

08:12.439 --> 08:13.472
No.

08:14.839 --> 08:17.000
Does he have any other news for me?

08:17.000 --> 08:18.519
nothing.

08:19.519 --> 08:21.879
You should leave.
If you don't, I'll have to kick you out.

08:32.128 --> 08:33.219
Stop pretending. It doesn't work.

08:33.219 --> 08:35.200
Master Rong and I will never trust you again.

08:39.360 --> 08:40.448
I understand.

08:41.320 --> 08:44.200
Then tell him to take care.

08:45.519 --> 08:46.619
I won't bother him anymore.

08:46.619 --> 08:48.320
Don't say these hypocritical things.

08:48.320 --> 08:50.976
You are the worst person ever. Let's go.

09:00.840 --> 09:02.799
Xunxunan humiliates us like this.

09:02.799 --> 09:04.600
My sister is still waiting for us to rescue her.

09:05.240 --> 09:06.679
Father, please raise an army.

09:07.799 --> 09:08.896
nonsense!

09:09.559 --> 09:10.859
How could you start a war so hastily?

09:10.859 --> 09:13.060
This is a blatant provocation.

09:13.060 --> 09:15.780
Should we just let Ren Yinxiao be rude?

09:15.780 --> 09:17.200
Do you want your sister to die in a foreign country?

09:18.480 --> 09:19.520
when i leave,

09:20.679 --> 09:22.919
My sister is still locked in
that useless prince's yard.

09:23.600 --> 09:25.440
She couldn't even get a decent meal.

09:26.159 --> 09:27.360
If we don't act quickly,

09:27.960 --> 09:30.200
We may have to collect her body, father.

09:31.679 --> 09:32.736
I…

09:33.720 --> 09:34.919
I wrote a letter to Ren Yinxiao.

09:36.480 --> 09:38.539
What good does this letter do?

09:38.539 --> 09:40.020
It was obvious they were not afraid of us.

09:40.020 --> 09:41.240
Otherwise, they would not make such a move.

09:44.559 --> 09:45.799
Do you know what conscription means?

09:46.519 --> 09:48.039
Do you know
what preparations are needed for war?

09:49.840 --> 09:51.480
War is a conflict between two sides

09:52.720 --> 09:55.799
We can't just
jump in just because of one person.

09:58.039 --> 10:00.360
But - but she's your daughter.

10:01.559 --> 10:02.624
She is also my sister.

10:03.519 --> 10:04.540
She was given the title of princess.

10:04.540 --> 10:06.360
She now represents Jia Lin.

10:09.440 --> 10:10.959
what do you know

10:10.959 --> 10:12.639
Diplomatic and court affairs?

10:14.759 --> 10:15.872
you are right.

10:17.320 --> 10:18.919
i don't know anything about it

10:20.279 --> 10:21.759
But I know you're afraid.

10:22.688 --> 10:23.739
before you do anything,

10:23.739 --> 10:25.519
You always go to Xingxiang Pavilion
to ask Rong Gong.

10:26.399 --> 10:29.360
You are always cautious, timid, and careful.

10:29.360 --> 10:31.279
How can you achieve something significant?

10:31.919 --> 10:32.928
you…

10:59.328 --> 11:00.420
anything else?

11:00.420 --> 11:01.420
This is enough.

11:01.420 --> 11:02.496
OK

11:16.399 --> 11:17.440
Are you blind?

11:18.120 --> 11:20.559
Now you even dare to bully me?

11:43.360 --> 11:44.448
He Jiuling.

11:48.519 --> 11:49.568
what happened?

11:50.840 --> 11:52.240
You don't hate me now.

11:54.080 --> 11:55.104
I do.

11:55.759 --> 11:57.159
It's just that I'm not in the mood right now.

11:58.600 --> 11:59.680
He Jiuling,

12:02.000 --> 12:03.279
I have something to tell you.

12:12.440 --> 12:14.799
I don't believe a word you said.

12:16.279 --> 12:17.639
King Xunnan is not that kind of person.

12:22.000 --> 12:23.559
How do you know he's not like that?

12:25.639 --> 12:27.279
If you slander others again

12:28.600 --> 12:30.039
I'll teach you a lesson.

12:39.799 --> 12:40.832
I just remembered...

12:41.632 --> 12:42.739
gentlemen.

12:42.739 --> 12:44.480
You two are old acquaintances, aren't you?

12:46.480 --> 12:47.960
When I was still Prince Yong,

12:48.679 --> 12:49.696
He even proposed in the palace.

12:52.360 --> 12:53.879
Although he failed to marry you,

12:54.639 --> 12:56.320
You two are at least friends.

13:00.759 --> 13:02.200
He is really lucky.

13:03.200 --> 13:04.639
You two are at least friends.

13:07.759 --> 13:08.800
He Jiuling,

13:09.840 --> 13:11.600
Now there is no one to help my sister.

13:12.480 --> 13:14.480
can you help me if possible

13:14.480 --> 13:15.520
To save my sister?

13:16.080 --> 13:17.679
Sit here and make tea for you

13:17.679 --> 13:18.680
It was through gnashing of teeth.

13:18.680 --> 13:20.360
How dare you embarrass Miss He?

13:27.720 --> 13:28.960
Here you go, sir.

13:30.320 --> 13:31.559
- sorry.
- please.

13:32.360 --> 13:33.399
Before, my sister and I

13:35.960 --> 13:37.960
Did a lot of bad things to you.

13:39.600 --> 13:41.000
I always feel sorry.

13:42.039 --> 13:43.440
I sincerely apologize and will do my best

13:44.200 --> 13:46.120
To make it up to you.

13:46.679 --> 13:48.039
Apologize?

13:48.039 --> 13:50.320
Do you really think apologizing
can solve everything?

13:50.320 --> 13:51.820
Stop pretending you don't know
what's going on here.

13:51.820 --> 13:52.832
Tan.

14:03.840 --> 14:06.679
I can write
to you to ask about the situation,

14:10.688 --> 14:12.768
But there is nothing I can do.

14:19.720 --> 14:20.736
even so,

14:22.919 --> 14:24.440
You are the only one who can help me.

14:26.639 --> 14:28.860
My apology just now was sincere.

14:28.860 --> 14:29.919
From the bottom of my heart.

14:31.279 --> 14:32.320
If you need my help in the future

14:32.320 --> 14:33.559
with anything,

14:34.080 --> 14:35.180
Even help you reverse the case,

14:35.180 --> 14:36.279
You can come to me anytime.

14:36.279 --> 14:37.559
unnecessary.

14:37.559 --> 14:38.624
No.

14:39.600 --> 14:41.000
I will always remember this in my heart.

14:56.440 --> 14:57.600
You and Rong Yu are

14:58.919 --> 14:59.968
Much like now.

15:02.320 --> 15:03.519
If it were you before

15:04.960 --> 15:06.200
You would have laughed before

15:07.320 --> 15:09.080
And scolded me

15:09.080 --> 15:10.799
For those in this situation,

15:12.440 --> 15:13.440
but now you want

15:14.519 --> 15:16.840
sit with people you don't like

15:18.919 --> 15:20.039
Even invited me to tea.

15:22.000 --> 15:23.600
Although I hate to admit it,

15:24.639 --> 15:26.879
You and Rong Yu are actually a good match.

15:28.919 --> 15:30.519
What a fool.

15:30.519 --> 15:31.840
Do you intentionally make others angry?

15:32.600 --> 15:33.799
Jiuling, let’s go.

15:41.759 --> 15:42.784
He Jiuling.

15:44.879 --> 15:45.920
Can I…

15:47.320 --> 15:48.840
can i be your friend?

15:50.960 --> 15:52.519
We will never be friends.

16:20.200 --> 16:22.000
go out! You all go out.

16:53.440 --> 16:54.960
Cheng'an, it's me.

16:56.840 --> 16:57.856
Cheng'an.

17:03.679 --> 17:04.800
elder sister.

17:10.920 --> 17:12.359
I know you'll be fine.

17:13.240 --> 17:15.900
Cheng'an, I'm not just good at

17:15.900 --> 17:17.160
Pray to Bodhisattva for help.

17:17.664 --> 17:18.816
Believe me.

17:19.400 --> 17:20.576
In times of crisis,

17:21.720 --> 17:22.799
I can protect you too.

17:23.492 --> 17:25.000
[Jiang's Mansion]

17:25.000 --> 17:26.176
You lied to me, right?

17:27.552 --> 17:28.576
Things about the He family,

17:29.559 --> 17:31.240
It has nothing to do with our family, right?

17:32.480 --> 17:34.039
Otherwise, how could I not know anything?

17:36.079 --> 17:37.152
For such things,

17:37.799 --> 17:39.880
Do I need to tell you loud and clear?

17:42.000 --> 17:43.072
What now?

17:44.000 --> 17:45.480
Why are you telling me all this now?

17:47.392 --> 17:48.420
if you don't want me to know

17:48.420 --> 17:50.240
Why can't you hide it from me forever?

17:54.279 --> 17:55.360
Because in the future,

17:56.519 --> 17:58.319
person sitting on the throne

17:59.519 --> 18:00.576
It will be you.

18:06.079 --> 18:07.960
How could you say such rebellious words?

18:08.720 --> 18:10.240
Isn't your current position strong enough?

18:11.119 --> 18:13.839
Min, this is not
a question of whether it is enough.

18:14.480 --> 18:18.580
If I hadn’t gotten rid of the Nanjiang He family back then,

18:18.580 --> 18:20.920
Will our family still have its current status?

18:22.319 --> 18:25.800
If I don't stand at the highest position now,

18:25.800 --> 18:28.680
Is there any way out for our family?

18:29.880 --> 18:32.880
Min, it's time for you to know.

18:33.880 --> 18:35.160
I don't want to hear these words from you.

18:35.680 --> 18:37.319
I only know that when the He family is here,

18:38.960 --> 18:40.599
Our lives are just as beautiful.

18:41.640 --> 18:43.319
Why do you have to reach such great heights?

18:44.400 --> 18:45.440
What now?

18:46.319 --> 18:49.200
Shouldn't the most important thing now
be to rescue my sister?

18:49.200 --> 18:51.680
My sister is still waiting for us to rescue her.

18:52.200 --> 18:53.960
Now is the moment of truth.

18:54.640 --> 18:58.000
I won't allow anyone or anything
to ruin my plans.

18:58.000 --> 18:59.072
Not even your sister.

19:02.119 --> 19:03.440
So, you mean

19:04.359 --> 19:07.119
You only care about your future and goals,

19:07.680 --> 19:09.299
You and my sister get along very well

19:09.299 --> 19:13.024
Being bullied and self-destructing in Xunnan?

19:13.960 --> 19:16.200
After a while, I'll figure it out.

19:23.039 --> 19:24.759
So do you really want to do this?

19:26.440 --> 19:27.519
I can not believe it,

19:28.200 --> 19:30.039
At this time, my closest family members are actually

19:30.599 --> 19:32.720
More indifferent than the people I’ve hurt?

19:36.079 --> 19:37.088
Stop there.

19:41.119 --> 19:43.119
Do you think I don't worry or care about Lin?

19:43.680 --> 19:45.640
There is no turning back.

19:46.240 --> 19:49.039
Min, you don't want to destroy our whole family,
do you?

19:50.559 --> 19:51.584
I have no idea.

19:52.480 --> 19:53.504
I do not know anything.

19:54.759 --> 19:57.536
I just wish you hadn't told me all this today.

19:57.536 --> 20:00.240
- minute.
- Stop pushing me, Father.

20:33.920 --> 20:35.008
a stranger.

20:48.640 --> 20:49.720
Princess of Zealand.

20:59.759 --> 21:00.768
General He.

21:04.920 --> 21:05.952
Lord Jiuling.

21:43.428 --> 21:45.892
【Guozi Studies】

21:57.599 --> 21:58.624
——He Jiuling.
- Your Majesty.

22:00.000 --> 22:02.319
hurry up. We may be discovered soon.

22:02.319 --> 22:03.328
Jiuling, I…

22:06.759 --> 22:07.776
assassin!

22:08.480 --> 22:10.319
You go first, I'll stay behind. go!

22:12.039 --> 22:13.728
- go.
- There are assassins!

22:24.440 --> 22:25.440
Master Rong.

22:32.759 --> 22:33.760
Zhanping.

22:36.352 --> 22:37.400
What's wrong?

22:37.400 --> 22:39.599
Prepare your horses to fight against General Yan.

22:51.440 --> 22:53.240
Let go of the emperor!

22:54.640 --> 22:56.640
You all go!

23:19.160 --> 23:20.359
He-He Jiuling.

23:22.599 --> 23:23.648
move.

23:26.559 --> 23:28.680
Has it always been you?

23:30.880 --> 23:32.640
The palace was crowded with our people.

23:32.640 --> 23:34.199
There is no way you can escape.

23:34.199 --> 23:36.880
You are asking for death.

23:37.599 --> 23:38.799
We'll wait and see

23:39.640 --> 23:41.080
Who will bear the consequences.

23:41.080 --> 23:43.039
He Jiuling, you'll die.

23:44.039 --> 23:45.120
Rebellious.

23:48.680 --> 23:49.760
He Jiuling.

23:55.119 --> 23:59.200
How dare you traitors kidnap His Majesty.

24:01.640 --> 24:03.980
He Jiuling asked them to put down
their weapons quickly.

24:03.980 --> 24:05.400
I will beg my father to spare your life.

24:06.759 --> 24:07.776
Jiuling.

24:08.920 --> 24:09.920
Your Majesty,

24:10.640 --> 24:11.712
We need to wait.

24:12.319 --> 24:15.080
He Jiuling, I beg you.

24:15.080 --> 24:16.559
Are you still insisting?

24:17.160 --> 24:18.419
Kill them all.

24:18.419 --> 24:19.720
- stop.
- No.

24:20.519 --> 24:21.600
His Majesty is still among them.

24:24.640 --> 24:25.696
shooting.

24:53.440 --> 24:55.400
stop. Everyone stop.

25:02.240 --> 25:03.360
Jiuling.

25:09.839 --> 25:10.912
About the He family,

25:12.319 --> 25:13.559
I asked my father.

25:16.000 --> 25:17.120
I'm very sorry.

25:17.839 --> 25:19.480
I can't do anything for you.

25:21.400 --> 25:22.464
I…

25:23.480 --> 25:24.480
If I…

25:25.440 --> 25:26.440
I knew it very early,

25:28.119 --> 25:29.599
I would have stopped my father.

25:35.519 --> 25:37.400
